AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-aws-profile-role-nodeLaunchConfiguration-0aee2f4
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-09d555bd07fee626c","subnet-05a2a78e51e64d710","subnet-025d723623fad5d05"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-8cde1de-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-8cde1de
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
